<paragraph id="B2113FE02DBD935FD3299C2AF14FAC64" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="993FA4A9474ED3E87FA81DCEB15468C3" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
This species is excluded from 
<taxonomicName id="879271378B3F60018DA09F5F191E95F1" class="Sordariomycetes" family="Ceratostomataceae" genus="Melanospora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Melanospora" order="Melanosporales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">Melanospora</taxonomicName>
due to its dark brown, non-translucent, setose ascomata and its small ascospores (4.5-12 
<normalizedToken id="EAE83820B76D0B423F60421620FDB5D9" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
4-7 
<normalizedToken id="874DCFB698DED0A1168D20296682A066" originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
), which seem to indicate a closer relationship with 
<taxonomicName id="0ADF42642EDDA6F821002CE210C3C0C7" class="Sordariomycetes" family="Chaetomiaceae" genus="Chaetomium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Chaetomium" order="Sordariales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">Chaetomium</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
